will be punished by His Majesty.

60
00:03:33,220 --> 00:03:34,550
Since you've come this far,

61
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,550
I won't blame you for stealing the treasure map,

62
00:03:38,970 --> 00:03:41,010
