95
00:05:33,010 --> 00:05:33,850
Oh!

96
00:05:33,970 --> 00:05:34,970
Oops.

97
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:38,010
I should call him my darling now.

98
00:05:38,890 --> 00:05:41,350
He only belongs to me now.

99
00:05:57,470 --> 00:05:58,680
What's wrong?

100
